# ROBOT BRAIN - Cyberpunk Robot Controller App

## Project Overview
Premium mobile application for controlling ESP32-powered robots with cyberpunk aesthetic, voice AI, sequence recording, and custom command mapping.

## Tech Stack
- React Native 0.76+ with TypeScript
- react-native-ble-plx for Bluetooth
- react-native-reanimated for animations
- react-native-svg for graphics
- zustand for state management
- @react-navigation for navigation

## Project Structure
src/
├── screens/
│   ├── MainController/     # Main control screen
│   ├── CodeLab/            # Command mapping
│   ├── Sequences/          # Sequence library
│   ├── VoiceStudio/        # Voice AI training
│   └── Settings/           # App settings
├── components/
│   ├── LEDStrip/           # LED animation components
│   ├── HolographicJoystick/ # 360° joystick
│   ├── TactileSliders/     # Vertical sliders
│   ├── VoiceOrb/          # Holographic voice orb
│   ├── QuickCommands/      # Command matrix buttons
│   └── StatusBar/          # Top status bar
├── services/
│   ├── bluetooth/          # ESP32 communication
│   ├── voice/              # Voice AI service
│   ├── sequences/          # Sequence recording/playback
│   └── commands/           # Command mapping
├── store/
│   ├── useRobotStore.ts    # Robot state
│   ├── useSequenceStore.ts # Sequences
│   └── useSettingsStore.ts # Settings
├── theme/
│   ├── colors.ts           # Cyberpunk color palette
│   ├── typography.ts       # Fonts and text styles
│   └── effects.ts          # Visual effects (glow, glitch, etc.)
├── utils/
│   ├── ledAnimations.ts    # LED animation library
│   ├── bluetoothProtocol.ts # Message encoding/decoding
│   └── voiceParser.ts      # Voice command parsing
└── constants/
    ├── commands.ts         # Command definitions
    └── protocol.ts         # Bluetooth protocol specs

## Design Principles
- Cyberpunk aesthetic: Neon colors, glassmorphism, holographic effects
- LED Framework: Every UI element has LED indicators
- Visual Feedback: Every action has beautiful confirmation
- Infinite Flexibility: Custom command mapping for any robot

## Key Features
1. 360° Holographic Joystick with LED ring
2. Tactile Command God sliders (4 vertical sliders)
3. Voice AI with holographic orb
4. Sequence recording with timeline
5. Code Lab for custom command mapping
6. Real-time LED animations
7. Cyberpunk UI with glassmorphism


